## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

### Backend  
- **Language:** Python  
- **Framework:** FastAPI or Node.js (WIP)  
- **Vector DB:** Qdrant / Weaviate  
- **Text DB:** PostgreSQL  
- **Search:** Custom RAG pipeline  
- **Data Sources:** GovInfo, CourtListener, state legislature APIs  
- **Prompting:** LangChain / LlamaIndex (RAG architecture)

### Frontend  
- **Framework:** Next.js or Phoenix LiveView  
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (dark theme)  
- **Components:** shadcn/ui  
- **Languages:** TypeScript + Markdown rendering

